<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&lt;nitpick&gt;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&lt;/nitpick&gt;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>I find it kind of odd that rather than addressing Deeds as &quot;SCP-662-1&quot;, the interview addressed him as his unofficial title.</p>
